---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const title = "Remote Job Jumpstart Kit";
const description = "Complete 7-day action plan to land your first remote job - from resume to interviews to avoiding scams.";
---

<BaseLayout {title} {description}>
  <div class="kit-container">
    <header class="kit-header">
      <h1>Remote Job Jumpstart Kit</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">work anywhere. live everywhere.</p>
      <div class="download-cta">
        <p>Want the printable PDF version? Get the complete kit free:</p>
        <button class="btn btn--secondary" onclick="openDownloadModal()">Download PDF Kit</button>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="kit-layout">
      <nav class="kit-sidebar">
        <h3>Quick Navigation</h3>
        <ul class="nav-list">
          <li><a href="#quick-start" class="nav-link">1. Quick Start (7 Days)</a></li>
          <li><a href="#resume-blueprint" class="nav-link">2. Resume Blueprint</a></li>
          <li><a href="#zero-experience" class="nav-link">3. Zero Experience</a></li>
          <li><a href="#cover-letters" class="nav-link">4. Cover Letters</a></li>
          <li><a href="#cold-outreach" class="nav-link">5. Cold Outreach</a></li>
          <li><a href="#interview-prep" class="nav-link">6. Interview Prep</a></li>
          <li><a href="#scam-checklist" class="nav-link">7. Scam Prevention</a></li>
          <li><a href="#skill-sprint" class="nav-link">8. Skill Sprint</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="progress-indicator">
          <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-fill"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <main class="kit-content">
        <!-- Section 1: Quick Start -->
        <section id="quick-start" class="content-section card">
          <h2>1. Quick Start: Your First 7 Days</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">Your remote job hunt doesn't need to feel overwhelming. Here's a <strong>7-day action plan</strong> to get moving right now.</p>
          
          <div class="day-grid">
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>Day 1: Set Your Foundation</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li>Make a simple email just for job search: firstname.remote@gmail.com</li>
                <li>Create a LinkedIn profile (use a clear headshot + headline "aspiring [role] | ready for remote work")</li>
                <li>Install a free resume-ATS checker (like Jobscan free trial or Resumeworded)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>Day 2: Draft Your Starter Resume</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li>Use the "skills-first" template (see section 2)</li>
                <li>Don't wait for it to be perfect ‚Äî aim for <em>done in 1 hour</em></li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>Day 3: Pick a Role Lane</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li>Choose 1 of 3 entry-friendly lanes: customer support, admin/ops, marketing assistant</li>
                <li>Write down 5 keywords from real job posts in that lane</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>Day 4: Create Proof Without Experience</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li>Pick one mini-project from section 3</li>
                <li>Block 2 hours to complete and save your output (PDF, screenshot, link)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>Day 5: Set Up Your Tracker</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li>Download the job tracker template</li>
                <li>Log your first 3 applications (even imperfect)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>Day 6: Practice Outreach</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li>Send 1 LinkedIn message using the cold script (section 5)</li>
                <li>Goal: start a conversation, not beg for a job</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>Day 7: Apply Smarter, Not More</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li>Apply to 3 roles today</li>
                <li>Before hitting submit, run the scam-safe checklist (section 7)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pro-tip">
            <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Momentum > perfection. A few visible actions each day will get you interviews faster than waiting until everything is "ready."
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 2: Resume Blueprint -->
        <section id="resume-blueprint" class="content-section card">
          <h2>2. ATS-Friendly Resume Blueprint</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">Most remote job applications get filtered out by Applicant Tracking Systems (ATS) before humans ever see them. Here's how to beat the bots:</p>
          
          <div class="day-grid">
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>The Skills-First Template</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li><strong>[Your Name]</strong><br>Email | LinkedIn | Location (City, State)</li>
                <li><strong>PROFESSIONAL SUMMARY</strong><br>2-3 lines focusing on: relevant skills + remote work readiness + specific role target</li>
                <li><strong>CORE SKILLS</strong><br>‚Ä¢ 6-8 keywords from job postings<br>‚Ä¢ Mix of technical and soft skills<br>‚Ä¢ Include "Remote work," "Virtual collaboration"</li>
                <li><strong>RELEVANT EXPERIENCE</strong><br>Focus on achievements, not duties<br>Use numbers wherever possible</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>ATS Optimization Checklist</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li>Use standard fonts (Arial, Calibri, Times New Roman)</li>
                <li>Avoid graphics, images, or fancy formatting</li>
                <li>Include exact keywords from job posting</li>
                <li>Save as both .docx and .pdf</li>
                <li>Test with a free ATS scanner before applying</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 3: Zero Experience -->
        <section id="zero-experience" class="content-section card">
          <h2>3. Experience from Zero Playbook</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">No remote experience? No problem. Here's how to create proof of your capabilities:</p>
          
          <div class="day-grid">
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>Customer Support Mini-Project</h3>
              <p><strong>Time needed:</strong> 2 hours</p>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li>Pick a real company's FAQ page</li>
                <li>Write 3 different response templates for common issues</li>
                <li>Include: acknowledgment, solution, follow-up</li>
                <li>Save as PDF to show in interviews</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>Marketing Assistant Portfolio</h3>
              <p><strong>Time needed:</strong> 3 hours</p>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li>Choose a small local business without social media</li>
                <li>Create 2 weeks of post ideas</li>
                <li>Include captions, hashtags, posting times</li>
                <li>Present in a simple Google Sheet</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 4: Cover Letters -->
        <section id="cover-letters" class="content-section card">
          <h2>4. Cover Letter Angles</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">Three proven approaches that work for remote job applications:</p>
          
          <div class="day-grid">
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>The Problem Solver</h3>
              <p><strong>When to use:</strong> When you can identify a specific company challenge</p>
              <p><em>"I noticed [Company] recently expanded to new markets. Having helped coordinate logistics across time zones in my previous role, I understand the communication challenges this creates..."</em></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>The Culture Fit</h3>
              <p><strong>When to use:</strong> When company values align strongly with your background</p>
              <p><em>"Your commitment to work-life balance resonates with me. As someone who thrived during remote learning while managing family responsibilities, I bring both empathy and efficiency to customer interactions..."</em></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 5: Cold Outreach -->
        <section id="cold-outreach" class="content-section card">
          <h2>5. Cold Outreach Scripts</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">LinkedIn messages that actually get responses:</p>
          
          <div class="day-grid">
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>The Information Interview</h3>
              <p><strong>Subject:</strong> Quick question about remote work at [Company]</p>
              <p><em>"Hi [Name], I hope you're doing well. I'm exploring opportunities in customer support and really admire [Company's] approach to remote work culture. Would you be open to a brief 10-minute call to share your experience?"</em></p>
              <p><strong>Response rate:</strong> ~15-20%</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>The Value-First Approach</h3>
              <p><em>"Hi [Name], I came across [Company's] recent blog post about improving customer response times and found your insights really valuable. I've been working on a small project analyzing response patterns for remote teams..."</em></p>
              <p><strong>Best for:</strong> When you can reference their content or company news</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 6: Interview Prep -->
        <section id="interview-prep" class="content-section card">
          <h2>6. Interview Cheat Cards</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">Essential questions and answers for remote job interviews:</p>
          
          <div class="day-grid">
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>"Why do you want to work remotely?"</h3>
              <p><strong>Framework:</strong> Professional reasons + Personal fit + Company benefit</p>
              <p><em>"I'm drawn to remote work because it allows me to focus deeply on problem-solving without office distractions. I'm naturally self-motivated and have created productive systems for my current studies/work."</em></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>Questions You Should Ask Them</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li>"How does the team currently handle communication and collaboration?"</li>
                <li>"What does a typical day look like for someone in this role?"</li>
                <li>"How do you measure success for remote employees?"</li>
                <li>"What tools and systems does the team use daily?"</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 7: Scam Prevention -->
        <section id="scam-checklist" class="content-section card">
          <h2>7. Scam-Safe Apply Checklist</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">Protect yourself from fake remote job postings with this verification checklist:</p>

          <div class="scam-prevention">
            <div class="red-flags">
              <h3>üö® Immediate Red Flags (Run Away!)</h3>
              <ul class="checklist danger">
                <li>Upfront fees for any reason (training, equipment, background checks)</li>
                <li>Salary too good to be true ($50+/hour for basic data entry)</li>
                <li>Instant hiring without proper interview process</li>
                <li>Vague job descriptions with no specific duties</li>
                <li>Communication only through personal email (Gmail, Yahoo)</li>
                <li>Poor grammar and spelling in official communications</li>
                <li>Requests for sensitive information (SSN, bank details) upfront</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="verification-steps">
              <h3>‚úÖ Verification Checklist</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li><strong>Company research:</strong> Official website, business registration, real address</li>
                <li><strong>Employee verification:</strong> Find real employees on LinkedIn</li>
                <li><strong>Job posting check:</strong> Is it posted on company's official career page?</li>
                <li><strong>Communication audit:</strong> Professional email domain, proper grammar</li>
                <li><strong>Interview process:</strong> Multiple rounds, video calls, real people</li>
                <li><strong>Reference check:</strong> Can you find reviews or mentions of the company?</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="safe-practices">
              <h3>üõ°Ô∏è Safe Application Practices</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li>Use a dedicated job search email address</li>
                <li>Never provide SSN or bank details before a formal offer</li>
                <li>Research salary ranges for the role and location</li>
                <li>Trust your gut‚Äîif something feels off, investigate further</li>
                <li>Apply through reputable job boards and company websites</li>
                <li>Keep records of all applications and communications</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 8: Skill Sprint -->
        <section id="skill-sprint" class="content-section card">
          <h2>8. 30-Day Skill Sprint Plan</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">Build job-ready skills in 30 days with this focused learning plan:</p>
          
          <div class="day-grid">
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>Week 1: Foundation Skills</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li><strong>Days 1-2:</strong> Master Google Workspace (Docs, Sheets, Drive, Calendar)</li>
                <li><strong>Days 3-4:</strong> Learn Slack basics and professional communication etiquette</li>
                <li><strong>Days 5-7:</strong> Practice video call skills (Zoom, lighting, presentation)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>Week 2: Role-Specific Training</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li><strong>Customer Support:</strong> Zendesk or Freshdesk free training</li>
                <li><strong>Marketing Assistant:</strong> Google Analytics Academy (free certification)</li>
                <li><strong>Virtual Assistant:</strong> Project management tools (Asana, Trello basics)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>Week 3: Portfolio Building</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li><strong>Days 15-17:</strong> Complete one mini-project from Section 3</li>
                <li><strong>Days 18-19:</strong> Create professional portfolio or work samples</li>
                <li><strong>Days 20-21:</strong> Practice explaining your projects in interview format</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="day-card">
              <h3>Week 4: Application Readiness</h3>
              <ul class="checklist">
                <li><strong>Days 22-24:</strong> Finalize resume using ATS-friendly template</li>
                <li><strong>Days 25-26:</strong> Write 3 different cover letter templates</li>
                <li><strong>Days 27-28:</strong> Practice mock interviews (record yourself)</li>
                <li><strong>Days 29-30:</strong> Start applying to your first 5 positions</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="pro-tip">
            <strong>Free Learning Resources:</strong>
            <br>‚Ä¢ Coursera: Google Career Certificates (customer support, digital marketing)
            <br>‚Ä¢ LinkedIn Learning: Remote work and productivity courses
            <br>‚Ä¢ HubSpot Academy: Free marketing and customer service certifications
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- PDF Download CTA -->
        <section id="pdf-download" class="content-section card cta">
          <h2>Get the Complete Printable Kit</h2>
          <p>Want all of this in a beautifully formatted PDF? Download the complete Remote Job Jumpstart Kit including templates, checklists, and bonus materials.</p>
          <div class="download-actions">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="openDownloadModal()">Download Free Kit</button>
            <p class="download-note">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime. Join 2,000+ readers.</p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Download Modal -->
  <div id="downloadModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <span class="modal-close" onclick="closeDownloadModal()">&times;</span>
      <h3>Get Your Free Jumpstart Kit</h3>
      <p>Enter your email to receive the complete PDF guide plus weekly remote work tips.</p>
      <form class="download-form" onsubmit="handleDownload(event)">
        <input type="email" id="emailInput" placeholder="your email address" required class="form-input" />
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Download Link</button>
      </form>
      <p class="privacy-note">No spam, unsubscribe anytime. Join 2,000+ readers.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    /* Kit-specific styles */
    .kit-container {
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: var(--space-5);
    }

    .kit-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-teal-50) 0%, var(--color-coral-50) 100%);
      padding: var(--space-10);
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-teal-200);
    }

    .kit-header h1 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-5xl);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-teal-700), var(--color-coral-600));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
      color: var(--color-gray-600);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .download-cta {
      background: var(--color-white);
      padding: var(--space-6);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    }

    /* Modal Styles */
    .modal {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      z-index: 1000;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .modal-content {
      background-color: var(--color-white);
      margin: 10% auto;
      padding: var(--space-8);
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 500px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .modal-close {
      color: var(--color-gray-400);
      float: right;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      position: absolute;
      right: var(--space-4);
      top: var(--space-4);
    }

    .modal-close:hover {
      color: var(--color-gray-600);
    }

    .download-form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-4);
      margin: var(--space-5) 0;
    }

    .privacy-note {
      font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
      color: var(--color-gray-500);
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: var(--space-3);
    }

    /* Kit Layout */
    .kit-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 250px 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-8);
      align-items: start;
    }

    .kit-sidebar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 80px;
      background: var(--color-white);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      padding: var(--space-6);
      height: fit-content;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }

    .kit-sidebar h3 {
      color: var(--color-black);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
      font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    }

    .nav-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0 0 var(--space-5) 0;
    }

    .nav-list li {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    }

    .nav-link {
      display: block;
      padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3);
      color: var(--color-gray-600);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      border-left: 3px solid transparent;
    }

    .nav-link:hover {
      background: var(--color-teal-50);
      color: var(--color-teal-700);
      border-left-color: var(--color-teal-500);
    }

    .nav-link.active {
      background: var(--color-teal-100);
      color: var(--color-teal-800);
      border-left-color: var(--color-teal-600);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .progress-indicator {
      margin-top: var(--space-4);
      padding-top: var(--space-4);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    }

    .progress-indicator::before {
      content: "Reading Progress";
      display: block;
      font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
      color: var(--color-gray-500);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .progress-bar {
      height: 4px;
      background: var(--color-gray-200);
      border-radius: 2px;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .progress-fill {
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-teal-500), var(--color-coral-500));
      width: 0%;
      transition: width 0.2s ease;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .kit-content {
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .content-section {
      scroll-margin-top: 100px;
    }

    /* Basic grid for day cards */
    .day-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-5);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    }

    .day-card {
      background: var(--color-white);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: var(--space-6);
    }

    .day-card h3 {
      color: var(--color-teal-600);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .checklist {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .checklist li {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
      padding-left: var(--space-6);
      position: relative;
    }

    .checklist li::before {
      content: "‚Ä¢";
      color: var(--color-teal-600);
      font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
    }

    .pro-tip {
      background: var(--color-sand-50);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--color-sand-400);
      padding: var(--space-5);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      margin-top: var(--space-6);
    }

    /* Scam prevention styles */
    .scam-prevention {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-6);
    }

    .red-flags {
      background: var(--color-coral-50);
      padding: var(--space-6);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--color-coral-500);
    }

    .red-flags h3 {
      color: var(--color-coral-700);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .verification-steps {
      background: var(--color-teal-50);
      padding: var(--space-6);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--color-teal-500);
    }

    .verification-steps h3 {
      color: var(--color-teal-700);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .safe-practices {
      background: var(--color-gray-50);
      padding: var(--space-6);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gray-400);
    }

    .safe-practices h3 {
      color: var(--color-gray-700);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .kit-layout {
        grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
        gap: var(--space-5);
      }
      
      .kit-sidebar {
        top: 70px;
        padding: var(--space-4);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .kit-layout {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: var(--space-4);
      }
      
      .kit-sidebar {
        position: static;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
        top: auto;
      }
      
      .kit-header h1 {
        font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
      }
      
      .day-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <script is:inline>
    function openDownloadModal() {
      document.getElementById('downloadModal').style.display = 'block';
      setTimeout(() => {
        document.getElementById('emailInput').focus();
      }, 100);
    }

    function closeDownloadModal() {
      document.getElementById('downloadModal').style.display = 'none';
    }

    function handleDownload(event) {
      event.preventDefault();
      const email = document.getElementById('emailInput').value;
      
      if (!email) {
        alert('Please enter your email address.');
        return;
      }
      
      // Show success message and open PDF
      alert('Thanks! Opening your PDF download now.');
      closeDownloadModal();
      document.getElementById('emailInput').value = '';
      
      // Open PDF in new tab
      setTimeout(() => {
        window.open('/pdf/remote-job-jumpstart-kit?pdf=true', '_blank');
      }, 500);
    }

    // Close modal when clicking outside
    window.onclick = function(event) {
      const modal = document.getElementById('downloadModal');
      if (event.target === modal) {
        closeDownloadModal();
      }
    }

    // Scroll spy and navigation functionality
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      const navLinks = document.querySelectorAll('.nav-link');
      const sections = document.querySelectorAll('.content-section');
      const progressBar = document.querySelector('.progress-bar');

      function updateActiveNav() {
        let current = '';
        const scrollY = window.pageYOffset;

        sections.forEach(section => {
          const sectionTop = section.offsetTop - 100;
          const sectionHeight = section.offsetHeight;
          
          if (scrollY >= sectionTop && scrollY < sectionTop + sectionHeight) {
            current = section.getAttribute('id');
          }
        });

        navLinks.forEach(link => {
          link.classList.remove('active');
          if (link.getAttribute('href') === `#${current}`) {
            link.classList.add('active');
          }
        });

        // Update progress bar
        const documentHeight = document.documentElement.scrollHeight - window.innerHeight;
        const progress = (window.pageYOffset / documentHeight) * 100;
        const progressFill = document.querySelector('.progress-fill');
        if (progressFill) {
          progressFill.style.width = `${Math.min(progress, 100)}%`;
        }
      }

      // Smooth scroll for nav links
      navLinks.forEach(link => {
        link.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
          e.preventDefault();
          const targetId = this.getAttribute('href').substring(1);
          const targetSection = document.getElementById(targetId);
          
          if (targetSection) {
            const offsetTop = targetSection.offsetTop - 20;
            window.scrollTo({
              top: offsetTop,
              behavior: 'smooth'
            });
          }
        });
      });

      // Listen for scroll events
      window.addEventListener('scroll', updateActiveNav);
      updateActiveNav(); // Initial call
    });
  </script>
